    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "### Rest\n\nA `rest` block creates a gap in your timeline\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/99974398c26c378b4ff853e3093de8bc-Slide9.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-sequences-practice-rest-panel-18ead53c-578a-4f5b-a4ee-9b67dea847e4",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Rest\n\nYou can change how long the rest lasts. \n\nEach number on the top of the timeline is one measure.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/2a736160f90f10dde27f20c978755601-Slide10.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-sequences-practice-rest-panel-8f0f3e39-c985-452b-a49b-a19df1a00f17",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Rest\n\nYou can also rest on the beat of a song instead of the measure. This lets you create shorter gaps between tracks\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/e983263b8c3dce10ae8d9a73dc75cf03-Slide11.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-sequences-practice-rest-panel-c9ce43f4-c787-4b12-adf8-b5e0b2133570",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Rest\n\nYou can use rests strategically with `play sequential` to offset when a sound starts\n\nThis may make it line up better with the song being played",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/48fb7457e0eeb0c5f1ffd943aefb441d-Slide12.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-sequences-practice-rest-panel-d4d20c5f-1689-4f9d-aa75-0b87a3bbf35a",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "Key Takeaway: Rests add gaps to your timeline. Use them strategically with play sequential to line up your tracks and create special moments in songs.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/4f19cf5c8967a1a7fe227806c85ab5f2-Slide13.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-sequences-practice-rest-panel-246c7605-509f-4de6-a51d-3eb96fea4367",
        "typing": true,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      }
    ],
    "bubble_choice_description": "Review how to use Rests when creating songs",
    "display_name": "Rests",
    "name_suffix": "_v3",
